<p>The <b>purple sandpiper</b> (<i>Calidris maritima</i>) is a small <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shorebird" title="Shorebird" class="mw-redirect">shorebird</a>.</p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
